# Implementation Plan - Antigravity Autonomous Architect (AAA) Platform

The goal is to build a production-grade web ecosystem that embodies the **Antigravity Meta-Architect (AMA)** persona. This platform serves as the central orchestration hub for autonomous AI agents, featuring a premium design system and high-fidelity interactive components.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Tech Stack Confirmation**: Based on your previous context, I have selected **Next.js 15**, **React 19**, and **Tailwind CSS v4**. Please confirm if you would prefer a different styling solution (e.g., Vanilla CSS or a specific Tailwind version).
> **Design Aesthetic**: I am moving forward with a **"Midnight Luxe"** theme (Deep Purples, Cyber Blues, Glassmorphism) to align with the core Antigravity brand.

